description: A stunning home on the 20th floor, this 2 bedroom + study offers an incredible opportunity to make Boston's vibrant seaport neighborhood your home. The oversized window walls provide unbeatable views of the city and partial harbor views from the private terrace. The desirable floor plan boasts a large primary suite with custom walk-in closet and en suite marble bath. The sleek kitchen design boasts custom Italian cabinetry and Thermador appliances. Numerous upgrades can be found throughout the home including custom closets, Hunter Douglas electric window treatments, custom lighting, designer wallpaper and a tailor made wood slat wall in the primary bath. The unit comes complete with two valet garage parking spaces! Echelon provides sophisticated amenities in a full service, luxury building that includes 3 pools, an indoor basketball court, golf simulator, resident lounges, spa, hot tub, sky lounge and high end retail.
